.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, azalea, poppy, begonia, dahlia
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, fish, guinea-pig, mouse, snake
 1. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 7. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
 8. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who growsbegonia is not the owner of the mouse##6
10. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
11. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
12. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
14. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
15. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
16. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
17. the person who growspoppy is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the person who growsbegonia##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Flower   | marigold | dahlia | poppy | begonia     | azalea      | tulip |
| Pet           | dog         | fish        | mouse   | guinea-pig | chinchilla | snake    |

