.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, water
6 different games are played: whist, chess, billiard, backgammon, snooker, canasta
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 3. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person playing chess is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##7
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##7
10. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
13. the person playing billiard is the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | almond-milk | water | hot-chocolate | mirinda | 7up   |
| Game   | billiard  | backgammon      | whist | snooker     | canasta | chess |

