6 different games are played: go, scrabble, billiard, monopoly, backgammon, chess
 1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 2. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of pop is between the person playing backgammon and the fan of punk##2
 6. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 8. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of blues##7
 9. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
10. the person playing go is on the far right##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the fan of classical##1
12. the person playing billiard is not the fan of classical##6
13. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
14. the person playing billiard is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |  3   |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | punk | pop  | classical | electronic | gospel |
| Game           | chess  | scrabble  | monopoly | backgammon  | billiard     | go    |

