 3. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5
 4. the person eating zucchini is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
 5. the person eating banana is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 7. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
10. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
11. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is board-games##7

.:: Answer ::.
