.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, drawing, photography, traveling, video-games
There are 6 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, purple, fuchsia, brown, apricot
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes ebony##7
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 8. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
10. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5
11. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
14. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
15. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | drawing         | photography | collecting | camping   | video-games | traveling  |
| Color     | brown | fuchsia  | purple  | apricot | ebony  | lavender |

 